    excerpt: 'Warning: The Hidden Dangers of DIY Gutter Repair! Untrained fixes could cost you more than just money. Welcome to our latest blog post where we delve into the crucial world of gutter maintenance and repair, and why professional expertise is essential.',
    image: '/blog7.png',
